# Closed-loop odom-frame drive to a 2D target (x, y, yaw). Implemented
# by mw_skill_library/drive_to_pose_server as a 3-phase P-controller:
#   (1) rotate in-place to face (target_x, target_y)
#   (2) drive straight until distance < xy_tolerance
#   (3) rotate in-place to match target_yaw
# Coordinates are in /odom frame (no map dependency, no nav2).

# Goal
float64 target_x
float64 target_y
float64 target_yaw
float64 xy_tolerance 0.15
float64 yaw_tolerance 0.1
float64 max_linear_velocity 0.22
float64 max_angular_velocity 0.8
---
# Result
float64 final_x
float64 final_y
float64 final_yaw
bool succeeded
string message
---
# Feedback
float64 current_x
float64 current_y
float64 current_yaw
float64 distance_remaining
